Package: QuantileModels
Title: Estimation of Different Quantile Related Models
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Christian", "Jorge Carreiro", , "christian.jorge.carreiro@usc.es", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Estimation of different quantile models, at the moment only Conditional autoregressive value at risk (CAViaR) model and it's multivariate extension MVMQ-CAViaR are available, however, in further updates, other models and extensions will be included.
